narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: I learned more about how to engage in design processes in order to land on a version that you're happy with. In addition, I learned how to make a book along with an animation.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: A strength of this course is that it is extremely organized. Projects are paced out well, too. A weakness is that the class time is long!

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: I would definitely recommend this course to anyone with some background in graphic design. This class will challenge you and push you to think more deeply about your practice.
